fs.fibu2.view.model
Class BilancialMapping

java.lang.Object
  fs.fibu2.view.model.BilancialMapping

public class BilancialMapping
extends java.lang.Object

A bilancial mapping is an ordered map from EntrySeparators to BilancialInformation. Internally the mapping is kept as a HashMap and can be controlled in almost the same way, but there are also methods to retrieve the mappings in an ordered way, where the ordering is induced by the ordering on EntrySeparator used for JournalTableModel.

Author:
Simon Hampe
